oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: St. Paul and the Broken Bones with Williams Tyler at the Ryman Auditorium
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Ryman Auditorium (Nashville, Tenn.); St. Paul and the Broken Bones (Musical group); Tyler, William; Woodcuts (prints); Split Fountain Printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (black, pink, and split fountain, blue to green, on white) announcing the St. Paul and the Broken Bones with Ruby Amanfu at the Ryman Auditorium on February 16. Poster features woodcuts of a ship crash and a woman in a space suit.
